			<p>
				Corsen is a tool dedicated to 3D distances measurements
				within the cell developed to access the minimal distance
				between cellular objects (e.g. individual mRNA molecules
				and mitochondria surface). Corsen include 3D
				segmentation algorithm allowing extracting and
				characterizing cell objects to be processed - surface
				calculation, aggregates decomposition- for minimal
				distances calculation. A batch process is implemented to
				analyse cell populations making possible statistical
				analysis.
			</p>


